         The main thing i see alot nowadays, is Parents beating the sh*t outta there kids, and not showing them any love or anything of that nature. If ya use that kind of punishment on your child and totally treat him/her like trash, you should be ashamed of yourself. To me, this is one of the main things that breeds these kind of teenagers. Its worse then just plain out neglecting them. Dont get me wrong, your gonna put fear in thier eyes, but they are gonna grow to hate you and not show you a ounce of respect. IMO you have to show 10 times more love for your child, then the seriousness of a spanking.<br>
