Prime example:<br>
 <br>
Mom gets home from a 10 hour stressfull work shift. Is tired, has a headache, cant think straight etc (weve all been there).  Mom gets a call from neighbor saying her son broke thier window and they want money to fix it. atiredstressedoutpissedoffmom_001 finds her son and spanks him. Neither talk for the rest of the day, next day son is pissed off and home alone, then ignores the mom when she gets home, rinse repeat. <br>
